title: TABE Mathematics Practice Test Level A v2015.09
intro_text:
TABE Mathematics Practice Test Level A

Welcome to the TABE Mathematics Computation and Applied Practice Test for level A. The goal of this practice test is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the actual TABE Test and to give you a study plan for what you need to learn.

Questions 1-15 are math computation questions. No calculator is allowed for Questions 1-15.

Questions 16-30 are applied math questions. You will need a calculator for Questions 16-30.

You have 40 minutes to complete the test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.

Relax and do your best!
